<Page xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
      Title="The Eraser Tool Dialog">
    <FlowDocumentReader ViewingMode="Scroll">
        <FlowDocument>
            <Paragraph TextAlignment="Center" FontSize="16pt">
                The Eraser Tool Dialog
            </Paragraph>

            <Paragraph>
                The <Bold>Eraser Tool</Bold> dialog lets your change the dimensions and shape of the eraser.
            </Paragraph>

            <BlockUIContainer>
                <Image Source="ErasertToolDialog.png" Stretch="None"/>
            </BlockUIContainer>

            <Paragraph>
                Uset the <Bold>Width</Bold> and <Bold>Height</Bold> fields to specify the dimensions of the eraser in points 
                (1/72<Run BaselineAlignment="Subscript">nd</Run> inch).
            </Paragraph>

            <Paragraph>
                Use the <Bold>Rotation</Bold> filed to specify a rotation of the eraser. The rotation only makes sense when the horizontal and vertical dimensions of the eraser are unequal.
            </Paragraph>
        </FlowDocument>
    </FlowDocumentReader>
</Page>